title: 2 Virginia prison supervisors named in death of a disabled inmate in amended suit
description: The new, amended lawsuit now includes Capt. Travis S. Poston and now-former Marion Warden Jeffery Artrip as defendants along with the five previously named prison officers.

title: North Korea launches ballistic missile, thought capable of hitting distant US bases
description: North Korea fired a suspected intermediate-range ballistic missile toward the sea on Sunday, South Korea's military said.
